---
title: Sweet Chili Thai Turkey over Rice with Snow Peas and Tangy Mango-Pepper Salsa
description: This turkey dish is just as ready for summer as we are, thanks to a tropical mango salsa! The juicy tender turkey, glazed with sweet Thai chili sauce and served over creamy coconut rice, will have you dancing in your kitchen!
